node.hospital_zh: 雅麗氏何妙齡那打素醫院
node.hospital_en: Alice Ho Miu Ling Nethersole Hospital
node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，7 月 12 乘搭國泰港龍航空 KA734 由印度抵港，沒有病徵，由檢疫中心送院。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health and arrived in Hong Kong from India via Cathay Dragon flight KA 734. He has no symptoms and was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre.
